200</Height><Bytes>9091</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1013/hotel1254864-lounge.thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>70</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2233</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>LobbyRestaurantAndBar</PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/1013/hotel1254864-main.jpg</Url><Width>200</Width><Height>200</Height><Bytes>12815</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1013/hotel1254864-main.thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>70</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2234</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>Laje de Pedra Mountain Village is a friendly 3-star superior resort offering contemporary accommodation near the heart of Canela. Highlights include a spa, indoor and outdoor swimming pools and two restaurants. Sao Jose is a pleasant residential area with an abundance of green space. Close to the city centre, it offers easy access to a good variety of restaurants, bars and shops. Nearby places of interest include Parque do Caracol, the Cathedral of Our Lady of Lourdes and Cascata do Caracol. The regional park, in which the hotel is located, also offers many opportunities for outdoor recreational activities. The hotel is housed in a collection of mid-rise buildings which sit amongst lush green landscaped gardens within a regional park. Facilities include indoor and outdoor swimming pools, tennis and sports courts and a spa where guests can indulge in a beauty or massage treatment. Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the premises. Studio Premium rooms are cosy and decorated in a contemporary style with warm colours and dark wood ceiling beams. They feature a well-equipped kitchenette with cooker, microwave, washing machine and fridge and a sitting area with a sofa and a fireplace. They have a view of the mountains. The en-suite bathrooms feature a bathtub with integrated shower or a walk-in shower. The two restaurants offer national and international cuisine. Refreshing drinks can be enjoyed at the pool and lounge bars. Free parking is possible onsite.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>NonSmokingRoom</Code><Text>Non smoking rooms</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Parking</Code><Text>Parking</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>InHouseDining</Code><Text>Hotel restaurant</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>InHouseBar</Code><Text>Hotel bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MeetingRooms</Code><Text>Meeting rooms</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>SatelliteTV</Code><Text>Satellite TV</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditionedRooms</Code><Text>Air-conditioned rooms</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>BreakfastRoom</Code><Text>Breakfast room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HotelSafe</Code><Text>Central hotel safe</Text></Amenity><Rating><System>Stars</System><Score>30</Score><Description>Three star</Description></Rating><Rank>1</Rank></HotelElement>